Introduction

MuuTive (Korean: 뮤티브), formerly called PBT (Professional Blessed Terrific), was a pre-debut four-member multinational girl group formed by GKMNEO and co-managed by Padox_Sori. They released the pre-debut single “aHHa” on July 22, 2022. They also had a Japanese debut scheduled on October 14, 2022.

Sometime in May 2022, Gulnazar parted ways with the group but remained a trainee in the company. In May 2023, the group’s webpage was removed from GKMNEO’s official website, and only members Jimin and Ahryung were listed as solo artists of the company, indicating that the group had silently disbanded.
